o |first1=S. |last2=de Holanda |first2=P.C. |last3=Saa |first3=A. |title=Neutrino primordial Planckian black holes |journal=Physics Letters |date=2021 |volume=B822 |pages=136670 |doi=10.1016/j.physletb.2021.136670 |issn=0370-2693|bibcode=2021PhLB..82236670C |s2cid=244196281 }}</ref>
